headline: Renewables stocks rally as U.S. Senate drops excise tax
summary: Investing.com -- Renewable energy stocks surged after the U.S. Senate removed a widely criticized excise tax from its sweeping GOP tax bill, offering relief to a sector that had feared significant headwinds under the Trump administration.
